<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= siteMetadata.language %>">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= meta.title %></title>
    <meta name="description" content="<%= meta.description %>" />
    <meta name="keywords" content="<%= meta.keywords %>" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="<%= meta.canonical %>" />

    <meta property="og:type" content="<%= meta.openGraph.type %>" />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="<%= siteMetadata.name %>" />
    <meta property="og:title" content="<%= meta.title %>" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="<%= meta.description %>" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="<%= meta.openGraph.url %>" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="<%= meta.openGraph.image %>" />

    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="<%= meta.title %>" />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="<%= meta.description %>" />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="<%= meta.openGraph.image %>" />

    <script type="application/ld+json">
      <%- JSON.stringify(meta.structuredData, null, 2) %>
    </script>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="page">
    <div class="background-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <header class="site-header">
      <div class="brand">
        <span class="brand-mark" aria-hidden="true">⬤</span>
        <span class="brand-name"><%= siteMetadata.name %></span>
      </div>
      <nav aria-label="주요 섹션">
        <ul class="nav-list">
          <% navigationLinks.forEach((item) => { %>
          <li><a href="<%= item.href %>"><%= item.label %></a></li>
          <% }); %>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section id="hero" class="hero">
        <div class="hero__content">
          <p class="badge">Running Rabbit Official</p>
          <h1><%= heroContent.heading %></h1>
          <p class="lede"><%= heroContent.subheading %></p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="cta" href="<%= heroContent.cta.href %>"><%= heroContent.cta.label %></a>
            <a class="cta ghost" href="#policy">운영 정책 보기</a>
          </div>
          <ul class="hero-highlights" aria-label="운영 하이라이트">
            <li>강남역 11번 출구 도보 3분</li>
            <li>프라이빗 룸 & 무드 조명 완비</li>
            <li>24시간 예약·상담 가능</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <aside class="hero__card" aria-label="예약 현황 요약">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div>
              <p class="eyebrow">오늘의 예약 현황</p>
              <p class="card-title">강남 달토 · 달리는토끼</p>
            </div>
            <span class="status status-live">상담 가능</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="info-list">
            <li>
              <span>운영시간</span>
              <strong>매일 18:00 ~ 06:00</strong>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span>예약 채널</span>
              <strong>전화·메신저 상시 응대</strong>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span>주소</span>
              <strong>강남역 인근 (자세한 위치 안내)</strong>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="card-actions">
            <a class="cta full" href="tel:01000000000">지금 전화하기</a>
            <p class="helper">방문 일정·인원을 알려주시면 바로 배정해드립니다.</p>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </section>

      <section class="section-grid" aria-label="브랜드 섹션">
        <% sections.forEach((section) => { %>
        <article id="<%= section.id %>" class="content-card">
          <div class="section-header">
            <p class="eyebrow"><%= section.title %></p>
            <h2><%= section.summary %></h2>
          </div>
          <ul class="bullet-grid">
            <% section.bullets.forEach((bullet) => { %>
            <li><%= bullet %></li>
            <% }); %>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <% }); %>
      </section>

      <section class="gallery" aria-label="공간 미리보기">
        <div class="gallery__header">
          <p class="eyebrow">Mood & Space</p>
          <h3>달토·달리는토끼의 무드와 조명을 먼저 만나보세요.</h3>
          <p class="lede">프리미엄 라운지 감성을 담은 공간을 직접 확인하고 예약하세요.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery__grid">
          <figure>
            <img src="/images/dalto/룸3.jpg" alt="라운지 룸 무드 조명" />
            <figcaption>무드 조명과 사운드가 조화로운 룸</figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure>
            <img src="/images/dalto/룸6.jpg" alt="프리미엄 룸 좌석" />
            <figcaption>비즈니스·친목에 적합한 프라이빗 좌석</figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure>
            <img src="/images/dalto/goldblue.avif" alt="네온 사인 포토존" />
            <figcaption>브랜드 아이덴티티를 살린 포토존</figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">문의</p>
        <p>방문 일정, 인원, 원하는 분위기를 알려주시면 친절히 안내드립니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-meta">
        <span><%= siteMetadata.name %></span>
        <span>·</span>
        <span>강남 달토 · 달리는토끼 공식 홈페이지</span>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
